comments.message:
Added a code path to allow an entry like this in the Exposes directive:
```
{
  "T": {
    "Key1": "Value1",
    "Key2": "Value2",
    ...
  }
}
```

It's essentially identical to the following:
```
{
  "Type": "T",
  "Key1": "Value1",
  "Key2": "Value2",
  ...
}
```
(Notably, the type of "Exposes" is a json::array so each entry has to be its own object, thus the "dictionary in dictionary" in the new method)
